GET {{KafkaDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/topics/user-events/metadata
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get topic metadata for orders
GET {{KafkaDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/topics/orders/metadata
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get topic metadata for payments
GET {{KafkaDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/topics/payments/metadata
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Get topic metadata for notifications
GET {{KafkaDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/topics/notifications/metadata
