###

### 7. Get topic metadata for order-processing.DLQ
GET {{KafkaDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/topics/order-processing.DLQ/metadata
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Create custom topic (example)
POST {{KafkaDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "custom-test-topic",
  "numPartitions": 5,
  "replicationFactor": 1,
  "configs": {
    "retention.ms": "604800000",
    "compression.type": "gzip"
  }
}

###

### 9. Get metadata for custom topic
GET {{KafkaDemo.API_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/topics/custom-test-topic/metadata
Accept: application/json

